At 5thWatch, we value your privacy and understand the importance of protecting your personal information. We want to clarify that we do not collect any data or personal information about you when you use our Google OS Wear Wear Face app (the "App"). This applies to "5thWatch" and all developers.
​
No Information Collected
Our App does not collect any data or personal information about you. We do not collect your device information, IP address, location data, usage information, or any other type of data.
​
No Information Shared
As we do not collect any data or personal information about you, we do not share any data or personal information with any third parties.
​
Security
We take the security of your privacy seriously.  We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect any changes in our practices or to comply with applicable laws. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
​
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please get in touch with us at
support@5thwatch.co.uk
